<h5 id="subject_750377">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d02c2b8ebfdf44378e526f6c0f474323&amp;topic=79084.msg750377#msg750377" rel="nofollow">Re: 【暗影狂奔第五版核心规则书翻译】创建人物 p.64 --</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_750377'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_750377'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #5 于:</strong> 2015-09-09, 周三 16:47:06 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_750377_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
