<h5 id="subject_750561">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d02c2b8ebfdf44378e526f6c0f474323&amp;topic=79084.msg750561#msg750561" rel="nofollow">Re: 【暗影狂奔第五版核心规则书翻译】创建人物 p.64 --</a>
