<h5 id="subject_764384">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d02c2b8ebfdf44378e526f6c0f474323&amp;topic=79084.msg764384#msg764384" rel="nofollow">Re: 【暗影狂奔第五版核心规则书翻译】创建人物 p.64 --</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_764384'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_764384'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #19 于:</strong> 2015-11-16, 周一 17:15:57 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_764384_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
